{"tid":2508404,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"一拳超人129回已經解釋左崎玉力量係「無限」","createTime":"2021-04-28T17:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T04:31:23.000Z","uid":188282,"like":8,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c1bca126d06d0a924d9276ecd58d37cdca836386","tid":2508404,"uid":188282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:35:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmV5S9Ye2SQK66o71UAMdnLYcAep7fRCGPZd9HJJeTFy6Z?filename=xwHEPLk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxwHEPLk.jpg&h=d64cdd62&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQgfoac1D3uqhfpafgqFQEgJbWMKqxzf9tchBeXjRgym9?filename=ZyCtH5N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZyCtH5N.jpg&h=413985d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基本原理係所有生物都有極限<br />\n<br />\n強大嘅非地球人生物亦有解釋<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVBXoTFC9KcXmkoVq76FhzJDefTDL8KkbkEfsVF6V2f2b?filename=R5zLLjX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5zLLjX.jpg&h=50aa030e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n飛利、布歐果堆<br />\n<br />\n撒亞人、人造人可以歸入呢堆潛能極強大類別<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmT2AAoiuvsQAe9F2DZjW6bzTRxCsiEU4pNUv6uijCCyt4?filename=PyrFzdL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPyrFzdL.jpg&h=278ed7b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好喇，關鍵係作者明確講崎玉唔同，佢唔屬於以上所有類別。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU6Xw6cqR4ZgwqgkByDhdBTRxayBwdfGJtH8iKXSbQj3T?filename=HjFruNw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHjFruNw.jpg&h=ca471685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWGrRP6iYcRYm6QiFt52eJJgKWcky5CLckfedQG6KDmCy?filename=rZVfn7P.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrZVfn7P.jpg&h=d6155bee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n崎玉力量無上限，因為佢已經打開左界限之門<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaDzdGR53t6eum71wkKMieAyVFKauhEKeWnCbhixUCHCW?filename=mLmNYHy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmLmNYHy.jpg&h=e839bad3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好喇<br />\n實有人會話撒亞人都冇上限，佢地可以不斷變身，可能超藍之後有超綠、超黑&hellip;<br />\n問題係每個變身都有自己嘅極限，即係超1、超2、超3、超藍etc,<br />\n不過官方都有為以上唔同顏色設定戰鬥力上限，<br />\n例如極意、悟空比達合體，官方都俾左數值<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVqFkfeDMySPRjx6iLxEhEw8Fg8uTt8ZZ13jr8BwNLrvZ?filename=cKknNF3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcKknNF3.jpg&h=829d5c1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ8gdkyqw3hDMQKY5CXH1xoR1UasCQCrP23zUToYMtvwE?filename=3VHNemd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3VHNemd.jpg&h=5774c97a&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n即係有限制器。<br />\n<br />\n另外有人話撒亞人可以靠頻死復活提升戰力，但龍珠41卷已經寫左潛能出晒嚟之後，頻死再滿血復活係冇用。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNNuCEfzSSA73QDChhovE9gDKxUeQTX6WsuWgjMTBMDL2?filename=gKreDK5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgKreDK5.jpg&h=09a3fd31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfSsHGvp3zQ1qZHu4gi668T5BrpixZ8eMbVeThHUMx2bF?filename=Zp8c9RE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZp8c9RE.jpg&h=685a6512&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n悟飯頻死滿血之後，力量冇提升。<br />\n<br />\n暫時係咁。"},{"pid":"098699331bf49d79aca06b9da0f6bd6be02c2db9","tid":2508404,"uid":25601,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:37:33.000Z","msg":"諗太多<br />\n一拳只係為左指導畫功既作品 劇情都係次要"},{"pid":"183df5fe83f46097cb1e3e56e967b9849ba4d569","tid":2508404,"uid":160592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:38:38.000Z","msg":"點解突破到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係因為100下掌上壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab38f7ba57dba23ad187574169c11686f68ff9e8","tid":2508404,"uid":198590,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"re